    <item>
      <title>日本央行通过区域报告暗示其仍将加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boj-signals-it-remains-on-rate-hike-path-with-regional-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上调了对两个地区经济体的评估，暗示其仍将考虑进一步加息，但同时也没有证据表明需要立即采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boj-signals-it-remains-on-rate-hike-path-with-regional-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:43:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购竞争对手后，Italgas 的目标是到 2030 年实现 28 亿欧元利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/italgas-targets-2-8-billion-profit-by-2030-after-buying-rival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Italgas SpA 表示，在达成收购竞争对手 2i Rete Gas 的交易后，其新计划的目标是到 2030 年实现近 30 亿欧元（33 亿美元）的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/italgas-targets-2-8-billion-profit-by-2030-after-buying-rival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛将明年美国经济衰退的可能性降至 15%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/goldman-cuts-probability-of-us-recession-in-next-year-to-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家表示，9 月份强劲的就业报告降低了美国经济衰退的可能性，因此未来一年美国经济衰退的可能性已回到 15% 的长期平均水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/goldman-cuts-probability-of-us-recession-in-next-year-to-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行降息后瑞典长期通胀预期上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/swedish-long-term-inflation-expectations-rise-after-riksbank-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在瑞典央行降低基准利率并为未来几个月进一步降息做好准备后，瑞典央行发布的一项调查显示，瑞典长期通胀率的预期有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/swedish-long-term-inflation-expectations-rise-after-riksbank-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:26:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价连续第三个月上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/uk-house-prices-climb-for-a-third-month-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈利法克斯的数据显示，由于抵押贷款利率降低和收入增加刺激更多买家进入市场，英国房价 9 月份连续第三个月上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/uk-house-prices-climb-for-a-third-month-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农林中央银行计划发行自发出亏损信号以来的首支美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/norinchukin-bank-plans-first-dollar-bond-since-flagging-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本农林中央银行聘请投资银行进行其首次潜在的美元债券发售，因为这家农业银行表示预计其在海外债券上的投资将遭受巨额损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/norinchukin-bank-plans-first-dollar-bond-since-flagging-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后，美国大幅降息的希望消退，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/gold-steady-as-investors-weigh-middle-east-tension-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中东局势持续紧张，且美国就业数据强于预期，削弱了美联储进一步降息半个百分点的预期，但金价仍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/gold-steady-as-investors-weigh-middle-east-tension-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 23:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注以色列对伊朗袭击的回应，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周油价开盘走低，市场等待观察以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击对伊朗进行报复，美国总统乔·拜登也不鼓励对伊朗油田进行袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势加剧 石油押注创两年来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/oil-bets-are-most-bullish-in-two-years-as-mideast-tension-flares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，石油期货创下一年多以来的最大涨幅。期权市场的狂热甚至更为强烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/oil-bets-are-most-bullish-in-two-years-as-mideast-tension-flares</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
